name: How to Sell Drugs Online (Fast)
overview: To win back his ex-girlfriend, a nerdy teen starts selling ecstasy online out of his bedroom -- and becomes one of Europe's biggest dealers.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: To win back his ex-girlfriend, a nerdy teen starts selling ecstasy online out of his bedroom -- and becomes one of Europe's biggest dealers.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: As Moritz and the MyDrugs crew ramp up their hustle, the online drug shop grows more successful — and even more dangerous.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: When Lenny's health takes a turn for the worse, the crew puts their differences aside to raise money for his treatment. But new threats loom.

episodes.name: Nerd Today, Boss Tomorrow
episodes.overview: When his girlfriend breaks up with him after spending the year abroad, Moritz schemes to win her back by snagging a stash of ecstasy.

episodes.name: Life's Not Fair, Get Used to It
episodes.overview: Lisa lands in trouble with her parents. Moritz reprograms MyTems into an online drug store and tries to make amends to Lenny.

episodes.name: Failure is Not an Option
episodes.overview: Business is booming, and Buba wants a piece of the action -- but the product is getting bad reviews. Lisa thinks Dan has been ignoring her.

episodes.name: If This is Reality, I'm Not Interested
episodes.overview: Moritz's reputation takes a hit. After discovering a troubling email, Lenny confides in a new friend. Jens enlists Moritz to crack a password.

episodes.name: Score Big or Don't Score at All
episodes.overview: Lenny sets up the clear web shop while Moritz secretly meets a new supplier in Rotterdam. But the friends don't see eye to eye about their future.

episodes.name: If You Are the Smartest One in the Room, You're in the Wrong Room
episodes.overview: Things begin to unravel the day after the party, and Moritz is forced to turn to his rival for help. Lisa has a change of heart.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: To win back his ex-girlfriend, a nerdy teen starts selling ecstasy online out of his bedroom -- and becomes one of Europe's biggest dealers.

episodes.name: Think Different
episodes.overview: After making a million euros, the guys decide they want out of MyDrugs, so a nervous Moritz goes to Rotterdam to break the news to their suppliers.

episodes.name: Where Do You Want to Go Today?
episodes.overview: Moritz wrestles with the secrets he's been keeping from Lisa. Dan thinks fast under pressure, and Lenny and Kira get closer.

episodes.name: Inspired by Real Life
episodes.overview: Inspired by the results of a career test, Moritz embraces his role as CEO — but loses his cool when Lenny suggests Kira join the team.

episodes.name: Buy It. Sell It. Love It.
episodes.overview: Following a dangerous standoff, the guys search for a way to convert their bitcoins into cash, and Moritz's many lies start to catch up with him.

episodes.name: Move Fast and Break Things
episodes.overview: Moritz confides in Lisa, who warns him to clean up his act. Later, a tempting offer from Goodtimes tests his loyalty to Lenny and Dan.

episodes.name: Don't be evil.
episodes.overview: The guys' rivalry heats up. At a party in Rotterdam, Moritz gets a rude awakening and tries to warn his friends.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: As Moritz and the MyDrugs crew ramp up their hustle, the online drug shop grows more successful — and even more dangerous.

episodes.name: A single failure, a little slip
episodes.overview: Under pressure from Goodtimes, Moritz races to rebuild MyDrugs during a school trip to the woods, but code bugs — and allergies — derail his progress.

episodes.name: A misdemeanor, a little trip
episodes.overview: Lenny helps Moritz with the site on one condition: that they keep their collaboration a secret. Meanwhile, Jens frets about his son's future.

episodes.name: Does this condemn me, lock me away?
episodes.overview: Moritz hires a high-priced business consultant. Kira and Dan come up with new ways to raise money for Lenny's medical treatment.

episodes.name: Before you turn the key, I have one more thing to say
episodes.overview: The guys take a road trip to Rotterdam. Marie asks Lisa to keep an eye on her brother. When Moritz crosses a line, Dan does damage control.

episodes.name: To make amends, maybe be friends
episodes.overview: To celebrate the end of their Abitur exams, the students throw a costume party at school — and things get a little out of control.

episodes.name: Everybody gets a second chance
episodes.overview: A high-stakes situation leaves the friends scrambling to figure out their next move.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: When Lenny's health takes a turn for the worse, the crew puts their differences aside to raise money for his treatment. But new threats loom.
